conversations.value: A photo of a subject like <sks>, but positioned in a grassy outdoor setting rather than indoors. The collar is darker and thinner. A photo of a subject like <sks> but with a shorter, more compact build. The fur is more uniform in length and color, predominantly orange-brown with white accents on the face, chest, and legs. The ears are smaller and more triangular, and the tail is curled and fluffy. The subject stands on green grass, appearing happy with a similar expression to <sks>.
